    "text": "Protect American Widows Act of 2024 or the PAW Act of 2024\n\nThis bill redefines surviving spouse for purposes of the applicable filing status of such individuals. It expands from two to five years amount of time a spouse must survive a deceased spouse in order to qualify for joint filing status as a married taxpayer.\u00a0 \u00a0"
